# b16bbacd01e14845a2e8dee68a7079d5
#: ../../developer-guide/architecture/architecture.en.rst:542
msgid ""
"Where ``CACHE_BLOCK_SHIFT`` is the bit width of the size of a basic cache"
" block (9, corresponding to a sector size of 512). Therefore the value "
"with current defines is::"
